      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You can move, make a ranged attack, and move again before your foes can react.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Dex 15, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.K1DuZQv4CKQHxnIk]{Mobility (Combat)}, base attack bonus +4.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a full action, you can move up to your speed and make a single ranged attack at any point during your movement. If you have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.MBNI94tbMoqizPUk]{Trick Attack (Ex)} class feature, you can take your movement from trick attack at any time during a trick attack (see page 93) with a ranged weapon (instead of only before).</p>\n<p><strong>Normal</strong>: You can move only before or after making a ranged attack, not both.</p>"
